snippet.title: Arcade Longplay - Star Hawk (1979) by Cinematronics
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the game Star Hawk for Arcade machines. Released back in 1979 by Cinematronics, the game is very nicel space shooter with resemblance to the movie Star Wars. Full 3D graphics with vectors.
